---
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SectionDivider from '../../components/SectionDivider.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="DAO Primitives Framework - SuperBenefit"
  description="A systematic approach to designing decentralized organizations as purpose-aligned networks of autonomous teams."
>
  <section class="project-hero">
    <div class="project-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container project-hero-content">
      <span class="project-label">Framework</span>
      <h1>DAO Primitives Framework</h1>
      <p class="project-subtitle">A systematic approach to designing purpose-aligned networks of autonomous teams</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionDivider from="charcoal" to="cream" />

  <section class="project-content">
    <div class="container" data-animate="fade-up">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>What is the Framework?</h2>
        <p>
          The Primitives Framework helps organizations design coordination systems that balance efficiency with innovation, autonomy with alignment, and flexibility with coherence.
        </p>
        <p>
          It provides organizational patterns (structural building blocks) and dimensional lenses (assessment tools) that can be combined to create governance and operational systems tailored to specific contexts.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>Who Is This For?</h2>
        <ul class="audience-list">
          <li><strong>Organization Designers</strong> - working on DAO governance and decentralized coordination structures</li>
          <li><strong>Facilitators</strong> - helping groups establish or evolve their governance and operational systems</li>
          <li><strong>Communities</strong> - transitioning from informal coordination to formal organizational structures</li>
          <li><strong>Developers</strong> - implementing governance systems and coordination infrastructure</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>Core Components</h2>
        
        <h3>Dimensional Lenses</h3>
        <p>Three perspectives for assessing organizational context:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Phase</strong> - Developmental stage (Conversation → Formation → Organization → Iteration → Completion)</li>
          <li><strong>Scale</strong> - Size and complexity (Collaboration, Coordination, Constituency, Network)</li>
          <li><strong>State</strong> - Transparent organizational state enabling coordination without centralized control</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Organizational Patterns</h3>
        <p>Four fundamental building blocks:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>DAOs</strong> - Purpose-aligned networks of small autonomous teams</li>
          <li><strong>Cells</strong> - Small autonomous teams with clear boundaries and purposes</li>
          <li><strong>Roles</strong> - Defined responsibilities that entities can take on</li>
          <li><strong>Tasks</strong> - Units of work that need coordination</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>The Process</h2>
        <p>The framework guides you through three phases:</p>
        
        <div class="process-steps">
          <div class="process-step">
            <span class="step-num">01</span>
            <h4>Discovery</h4>
            <p>Assess your group's current phase and scale. Map stakeholders and organizational context.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <span class="step-num">02</span>
            <h4>Design</h4>
            <p>Select appropriate patterns. Choose governance approach. Compose into functional structures.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step">
            <span class="step-num">03</span>
            <h4>Implementation</h4>
            <p>Deploy technical infrastructure. Establish operational systems. Iterate based on feedback.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>Resources</h2>
        <div class="resource-links">
          <a href="https://knowledge.superbenefit.org/artifacts/primitives-framework/concepts/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-link">
            <span class="resource-icon">📚</span>
            <span class="resource-title">Framework Concepts</span>
            <span class="resource-desc">Core ideas, dimensional lenses, and organizational patterns</span>
          </a>
          <a href="https://knowledge.superbenefit.org/artifacts/primitives-framework/implementation/group-facilitation" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-link">
            <span class="resource-icon">🛠️</span>
            <span class="resource-title">Facilitation Guide</span>
            <span class="resource-desc">Complete guide through Discovery → Design → Implementation</span>
          </a>
          <a href="https://knowledge.superbenefit.org/artifacts/primitives-framework/rpp-governance-case-study" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-link">
            <span class="resource-icon">📖</span>
            <span class="resource-title">Case Study</span>
            <span class="resource-desc">RPP governance implementation</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionDivider from="cream" to="charcoal" />

  <section class="project-cta">
    <div class="container" data-animate="fade-up">
      <h2>Want to learn more or get involved?</h2>
      <p>Reach out on Discord or explore the knowledge base.</p>
      <div class="cta-links">
        <a href="https://discord.gg/d2EeszTvVm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta-btn">Join Discord</a>
        <a href="https://knowledge.superbenefit.org/artifacts/primitives-framework/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta-btn cta-btn--secondary">Explore Framework</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .project-hero {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--color-charcoal);
    background-image: url('/images/brand-showcase.webp');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    padding-block-start: calc(var(--header-height) + var(--space-2xl));
    padding-block-end: var(--space-2xl);
    min-height: 50vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
  }

  .project-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      rgba(196, 64, 26, 0.7) 0%,
      rgba(245, 135, 44, 0.6) 50%,
      rgba(45, 45, 45, 0.95) 100%
    );
  }

  .project-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .project-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .project-hero h1 {
    color: var(--color-cream);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .project-subtitle {
    color: var(--color-cream);
    opacity: 0.9;
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .project-content {
    background: var(--color-cream);
    padding-block: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .project-content .container {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .content-block {
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .content-block h2 {
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-md);
  }

  .content-block h3 {
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    margin-block: var(--space-lg) 0 var(--space-sm);
  }

  .content-block p {
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.85;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-md);
  }

  .content-block ul {
    margin-block-start: var(--space-sm);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-md);
    padding-inline-start: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .content-block li {
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.85;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .audience-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .audience-list li {
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--color-cream-light);
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .process-steps {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-block-start: var(--space-lg);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .process-steps {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .process-step {
    background: var(--color-cream-light);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .step-num {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    opacity: 0.3;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .process-step h4 {
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .process-step p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.75;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .resource-links {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .resource-links {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .resource-link {
    display: block;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-cream-light);
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform var(--transition-fast), box-shadow var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .resource-link:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .resource-icon {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .resource-title {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .resource-desc {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .project-cta {
    background: var(--color-charcoal);
    padding-block: var(--space-2xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .project-cta h2 {
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .project-cta p {
    color: var(--color-cream);
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .cta-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.8em 1.8em;
    background: var(--color-orange);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform var(--transition-fast), background var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .cta-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    background: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .cta-btn--secondary {
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-cream);
    color: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .cta-btn--secondary:hover {
    background: var(--color-cream);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
  }
</style>
